title: HD Advance 3 PAL CD
description:
This is an alcohol 120% mds/mdf of the hard to find Hd Advance 3.
PAL CD version, burned it back to cdr using alcohol again and verified it worked on my ps2.
As soon as i can get my hands on a dvdrom that can fast skip errors i&#039;ll upload the dvd version too, i know it&#039;s not really needed if you have a modchip but i&#039;ll up it just for completeness.


This is for those of you with modchips, if you don&#039;t have one installed you need some kind of swaptrick to boot this, if you&#039;re planning on buying swap magic or anything like that to boot this you might just go ahead and buy this instead.
